'''Ar'jany Martha''' (born 4 September 2003) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Rotherham United F.C.|Rotherham United]]. Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Ajacied Martha nieuw gezicht in eerste selectie Advocaat bij Curaçao |url=https://www.vi.nl/nieuws/ajacied-martha-nieuw-gezicht-in-eerste-selectie-advocaat-bij-curacao |work=[[Voetbal International]] |date=9 March 2024 |language=nl}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Early career===
Martha, whose roots lie in Curaçao,<ref name="wfs" /> joined Spartaan '20 in the south of his native city of [[Rotterdam]] during his childhood.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Willemse |first1=Ricardo |title=Ar'jani Martha tekent contract |url=https://www.spartaan20.nl/arjani-contract/ |website=Spartaan'20 |language=nl |date=4 June 2019}}</ref> He later moved to the football academy of the professional club [[Sparta Rotterdam]], where he played for four years. Then Martha moved to the [[AFC Ajax|Ajax]] academy.<ref>{{cite news |title=Ajax contracteert drie jeugdspelers |url=https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/247043/ajax-contracteert-drie-jeugdspelers |work=NHNieuws.nl |date=4 June 2019 |language=nl}}</ref> Since the 2020–21 season he has been playing for the second team [[Jong Ajax]] in the second-tier [[Eerste Divisie]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Jong Ajax Skills Challenge #2 {{!}} Jaymillio Pinas en Ar'Jany Martha |url=https://www.ajax.nl/artikelen/jong-ajax-skills-challenge-2-jaymillio-pinas-en-ar-jany-martha/ |website=Ajax |access-date=8 April 2021 |language=nl-NL |date=8 February 2021}}</ref>

===Ajax===
On 2 November 2023, Martha made his debut for senior [[AFC Ajax|Ajax]] team, by starting in a 2–0 win over [[FC Volendam|Volendam]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ajax.nl/artikelen/debutant-martha-dit-is-een-droom-voor-elke-jongen/ |title=Debutant Martha: 'This is a dream for every boy' |publisher=AFC Ajax |date=3 November 2023 }}</ref> Later that month, he made his European debut, replacing [[Borna Sosa]] in the 77th minute of a 4–3 [[UEFA Europa League]] loss to [[Olympique de Marseille|Marseille]].<ref>{{cite news |title=PORTRAIT {{!}} Ar'Jany Martha: 'This is just the beginning' |url=https://english.ajax.nl/articles/portrait-arjany-martha-this-is-just-the-beginning |access-date=14 October 2024 |work=Ajax |date=2 December 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Tomassen |first1=Brent |title=Martha over beslissingen arbitrage: 'Bepaalde dingen hoeven gewoon niet te gebeuren' |url=https://www.ajaxshowtime.com/bijzaken-en-geruchten/martha-over-beslissingen-arbitrage-bepaalde-dingen-hoeven-gewoon-niet-te-gebeuren |access-date=14 October 2024 |work=Ajax Showtime |date=1 December 2023 |language=nl}}</ref>

===Beerschot===
On 31 July 2024, Martha joined [[Belgian Pro League]] club [[K Beerschot VA|Beerschot]] on a multiple-season contract.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.beerschot.be/nl/nieuws/beerschot-trekt-arjany-martha-aan|trans-title=BEERSCHOT SIGNS AR'JANY MARTHA|title=BEERSCHOT TREKT AR'JANY MARTHA AAN|website=www.beerschot.be|language=Dutch|date=31 July 2024|accessdate=31 July 2024}}</ref> He made his debut for the club on 2 August, replacing [[Thibaud Verlinden]] in the 81st minute of a 3–1 away loss to [[Royale Union Saint-Gilloise|Union Saint-Gilloise]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Union te sterk voor Beerschot: 3–1 |url=https://www.bruzz.be/actua/sport/union-te-sterk-voor-beerschot-3-1-2024-08-02 |access-date=14 October 2024 |work=BRUZZ |date=2 August 2024 |language=nl}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Somers |first1=Mats |title=Beerschot lijdt eerste seizoensnederlaag tegen efficiënt Union |url=https://www.gva.be/cnt/dmf20240802_95772939 |access-date=14 October 2024 |work=Gazet van Antwerpen |date=2 August 2024 |language=nl-BE}}</ref>

=== Rotherham United ===
On 30 July 2025, Martha joined [[EFL League One]] side [[Rotherham United F.C.|Rotherham United]] for an undisclosed fee, signing a three-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-07-30 |title=Ar'Jany Martha: Rotherham United sign versatile Beerschot defender |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/crkz4p5gjgro |access-date=2025-07-30 |website=BBC Sport |language=en-GB}}</ref>

==International career==
===Netherlands youth===
Martha was a youth international for the Netherlands.<ref name="wfs">{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldfootballscouting.com/schede-giovani-talenti/arjany-martha-talento-olandese-classe-2003/|title=Ar'jany Martha: talento olandese classe 2003|date=10 January 2020}}</ref>

===Curaçao===
On 9 March 2024, it was announced that Martha had been called up by [[Dick Advocaat]] to join the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]] as part of the 23-man squad for the training camp scheduled for 18 to 25 March 2024 in [[Alanya]], [[Turkey]], ahead of the teams [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – CONCACAF second round#Group C|2026 FIFA World Cup qualification]] campaign in June.<ref name="cura">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ad.nl/nederlands-voetbal/dick-advocaat-verrast-met-ajax-speler-arjany-martha-als-debutant-in-selectie-curacao~ae38f21a/|title=Dick Advocaat verrast met Ajax-speler Ar'jany Martha als debutant in selectie Curaçao|date=9 March 2024}}</ref>

